docs.text: Commands guide User commands create-user Create a user and returns its API key. Name Required Default Value Description -n, --name true The name of the user to add. -d, --duration false 365 The number of days before the API key expires. delete-user Delete a user from the system knowing its API key. Name Required Default Value Description --api-key true The API key of the user to delete. renew-user Add time to live to the API key of a specific user. Name Required Default Value Description --api-key true The API key of the user to renew. -d, --duration false 365 The number of days to live to add to this API key.
